---
title: Creamy Roasted Pumpkin Curry with Basmati Rice & Flaked Almonds
description: Enjoy a bowl of rich and creamy pumpkin curry, loaded with colourful veggies and aromatic spices. With a sprinkling of lightly toasted almonds to finish it all off, this delicious meal will beat your local takeaway joint!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-roasted-pumpkin-curry-3406929d.jpg
